avr_prep - AVR Preparation Scripts for The Heart Machine Project

This directory contains a number of scripts to prepare an AVR for use on The
Heart Machine node hardware.

set_clkout - used to set the FUSE bits on an atmega328p to enable the CKOUT
             signal which we use to drive the mcp2515 clock

set_eeprom_id - used to write the node ID to the eeprom (when we have decided
                on a spec!
